
Kinesis

Streaming
Real-time, fully managed, scalable

Kinesis Firehose
* transform & load streaming data
* load into Kinesis Analytics, Elasticsearch, Redshift, S3

Kinesis Analytics
* process and analyse streaming data with SQL
* recognises standard data formats, auto-parses data, recommends a schema

Kinesis Streams
* build custom apps that process and analyse data
* collect log data from servers, desktops, mobiles, etc
* server-side encryption & AWS KMS master keys

Use Cases
Netflix - monitors communications between applications


Example Architecture
[Website clicks] -> [Kinesis Firehose] -> [Kinesis Analytics] -> [Kinesis Firehose] -> [Redshift]
